			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I would recommend not assuming that the top and bottom eight scanlines are shown --- so don't put anything important there --- but not assuming that they are not shown either. If you can avoid showing garbage in any part of the screen, then by all means, do avoid it. As a PAL NES owner, I have always borne a grudge against game developers who just nonchalantly tolerate ugly scroll seams at the top and bottom screen edges.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

